      textEn: [
        "Premier Zhou, our beloved Premier,\nwhere are you, where are you?\nDo you know how we miss you —\nyour people miss you!",
        "We call to the mountains:\nPremier Zhou —\nThe valley echoes:\n“He just left, he just left,\nthe revolutionary road stretches a thousand miles,\nhe strides forward without rest!”",
        "We call to the earth:\nPremier Zhou —\nThe earth rumbles:\n“He just left, he just left,\ndon’t you see on the heavy heads of grain\nthe gleam of his tireless sweat…”",
        "We call to the forests:\nPremier Zhou —\nPine waves surge:\n“He just left, he just left,\nthe campfire glows red at the bivouac,\nthe loggers recall his warm, kind words.”",
        "We call to the sea:\nPremier Zhou —\nThe waves reply:\n“He just left, he just left,\ndon’t you see on the coastal soldiers\nthe greatcoat he draped with his own hands…”",
        "We searched the entire world.\nAh, Premier,\nwherever the revolution needed you,\nacross the vast earth\nyour deep footprints are everywhere.",
        "We return to the heart of our motherland,\nand before Tiananmen we call with deep feeling:\nZhou — Premier — Zhou —",
        "The square answers:\n“You are right here, right here,\nhere, here,\nhere…\nYou are forever with us\n— together, together, together…”",
        "You forever dwell where the sun rises,\nyou forever dwell in the hearts of the people.\nYour people, generation after generation, miss you!\nMiss you, oh, miss you\n— miss — you…"
      ],
