      textEn: [
        "When I was young,\nnostalgia was a tiny stamp —\nI was on this side,\nMother on that side.",
        "When I grew up,\nnostalgia was a narrow boat ticket —\nI was on this side,\nmy bride on that side.",
        "Later on,\nnostalgia was a small, low grave —\nI was outside,\nMother was inside.",
        "And now,\nnostalgia is a shallow strait —\nI am on this side,\nthe mainland on that side."
      ],
